reviewText: This video highlights the Bengals transformation of the ugly ducklings to the swans of the AFC.  It follows the Bengals rise to the top of the AFC and come up one Louis Billups dropped interception from winning Super Bowl XXIII.  Also, this is the second Bengals AFC Championship...and the little brownies have zero AFC Championships and zero Super Bowl Appearances.  WHO-DEY!!!! WHO-DEY? WHO-DEY, think they gonna beat dem Bengals, Where they play? In the Jungle...Afraid of NOBODY!!!
